<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_43_r1l8">Hercʒog <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Oſterreıch </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_43_r1l9">Gnedıger 
<del rend="strikethrough">hercʒog </del> herre / VVir ſenden cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleuhtickeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l10">Hanſen Camrer vnd <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Prager vnſer burger vnd <expan>dẏen<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l11">mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden cʒureden von der hab vnd kauffmanſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l12">wegen als her <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von flednicʒ vnd her <expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von VVeyſpriach </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l13">den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in <expan>ewre<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan> herſchaft vnd <expan>gepiete<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l14">auch die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dabey <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough"> de </del> dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_43_r1l17"><expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_43_line_1576491836111_8344">burger vnd </ab></add> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> / in <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>en</ex></expan> etc ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_43_r1l18">Hercʒog <expan>Ernſt<ex>en</ex></expan> von Oſterreich <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_43" id="21r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Osterreich </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger herre, wir senden czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        durchleuhtickeit Hansen Camrer und <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Prager,
                        unser burger und <expan>dyen<ex>er</ex></expan>, mit
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden czureden von der hab und
                        kauffmanschaft wegen, als her <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Flednicz
                        und her <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Weyspriach den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in <expan>ewre<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>land<ex>en</ex></expan>, herschaft und
                            <expan>gepiete<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dabey <expan>gefange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz die
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>burger und</add>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Ernst<ex>en</ex></expan> von Osterreich
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
